2000-07-11  Ian Campbell  <ijc25@cam.ac.uk>
	* libbalsa/body.c:
	* libbalsa/body.h:
	* libbalsa/libbalsa.c:
	* libbalsa/libbalsa.h:
	* libbalsa/libbalsa_private.h:
